name: general research use
definition: This data use limitation indicates that use is allowed for general research use for any research purpose.

name: health or medical or biomedical research
definition: This data use limitation indicates that use is allowed for health/medical/biomedical purposes; does not include the study of population origins or ancestry.

name: disease-specific research
definition: This data use limitation indicates that use is allowed provided it is related to the specified disease.

name: no restriction
definition: This data use limitation indicates there is no restriction on use.

name: population origins or ancestry research only
definition: This data use limitation indicates that use of the data is limited to the study of population origins or ancestry.
